w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/saltburn_mansion_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在一名当地人发布了如何访问该网站的视频后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tiktok">TikTok</a>用户纷纷涌向电影<a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;ved=2ahUKEwijwbGCi86DAxVqhf0HHdknAqsQFnoECBIQAQ&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nme.com%2Ffilms%2Fsaltburn&amp;usg=AOvVaw2WCtWxmy9wm3NXcsi22UKw&amp;opi=89978449"><i>《Saltburn》</i></a>中现实生活中的豪宅。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="186" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/saltburn-review-party-with-the-poshos-in-the-naughty-noughties-3541554"><b>“Saltburn”评论：与淘气的上世纪九十年代的贵族们一起聚会</b></a></li></ul><p>电影制片人选择位于北安普敦郡的德雷顿宅邸作为埃默拉尔德·芬内尔新电影后期部分的拍摄地。</p><p>现在，住在该地点附近的瑞安·威廉姆斯 (Rhian Williams) 在 TikTok 上发布了一系列视频，概述了“如何前往索尔特本”并参观该房产。 </p><figure id="attachment_3567666" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3567666" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3567666" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/saltburn_cast_2024.jpg" alt="《索尔特伯恩》导演埃默拉尔德·芬内尔在片场与演员们交谈" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/saltburn_cast_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/saltburn_cast_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/saltburn_cast_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/saltburn_cast_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont